column5: Hey Dave Luke here, just wondering when you are heading up to Nipawin.

Hi Luke thanks for getting back. I was up on thurs. fri. and sat. it was very very slow. would you send me an email at [email protected] I would like to ask you about a thing or two. I should be back up on oct. 5, 6 7th...if not sooner. Are you fishing the vanity? lets chat. em. me. p.s. i bought a new boat in 06 a 1700explorer tiller w/ f75. not a ranger,lol but i like it. pls. email. Dave Q.
